Task Force X is back! The group of expendable villains who are DYING to save the world have returned but with a new coat of paint courtesy of Guardians of The Galaxy director James Gunn. Gone are the neon and grunge of 2016 and instead we get more than a bit of blood and gore in this R Rated take on the doomed team. Join us as we discuss the highs and lows of the film and decide which we prefer more in this deep dive and spoiler-filled review of The Suicide Squad!

